    <svcman/>
    <svcproc svcproctype="describe" graphiccount="0">
        <title>Heated Fuel Filter</title>
        <para>The fuel filter collects and removes moisture and contamination from the fuel in the vehicle's system
            before the fuel reaches the engine. The heater and thermal switch assembly, located in the fuel filter,
            prevents "gel-up" in the filter during cold weather operation.
        </para>
    </svcproc>
